title: Episode 176 - Adventures in Cross Cultural Dating (ft. Melanie Curtin)
description: Ever dated someone from a different background, or from a different country? What's sex and relationship like with a language barrier? Melanie and I get down and dirty in terms of our experiences as North Americans dating in Western and Eastern Europe, South America, Japan, the Caribbean, and beyond. If you've ever had sex or dated someone abroad (or wondered what it's like) you'll enjoy this lively discussion.
